Assemble
* build a 'house', 'desert', etc.
* Each player contributes a piece to the construction
* The game is over when the construction is built
* Each player receivers the construction as a sticker
* Constraints could exist: for example
    * Food preferences
    * Style preferences

Word Association

Keep the ball up

RPG battle

Puzzle Swap

Types of events
* Real-time, small group
* Real-time, global or large group
* Asynchronous, street-pass esque
* Asynchronous, global
* Asynchronous, small group